 hairstyles and interior and exterior design. Both are glamorous women who always dress up in glamorous outfits. They rarely dress down. I once saw Tracy dress up in eighties clothing for a party while Samantha was in superman costume. Both of them have a glamorous job and career. Tracy has got a supporting role in the upcoming television series while Samantha has got a leading role in it. She plays the role of a doctor in it. I consider acting a worthwhile career. By the way I don't think Jason needs to dress up to go to work. A polo shirt and shorts are fine. Just dress down to go to work. He thinks if a girl without makeup still looks pretty then she's pretty. And there shouldn't be a big difference between with makeup and without."},{"pid":"439a204c6317cf440d29363edf50041baab0af2d","tid":1781260,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n台灣女人身材同樣既基因應該全亞洲最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac1790f88007dd4acd9e7185c16fc44ffc60a7c","tid":1781260,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e42445c702707c72585eaa6ef5d4e2f5238ca7e","tid":1781260,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"台灣美食大多油膩、飲料也很甜，但她們身材卻保持完美<br />\n<br />\n我去過台灣唔覺得佢地特別瘦，但一定唔係肥<br />\n究竟點解日日食咁油膩嘅嘢都keep到身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:33:22.000Z","msg":"台妹個身有陣油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本妹個身陣香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfc294e058f17e90b045e2af39e8ab072a5ff4d","tid":1781260,"uid":14262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"439a204c6317cf440d29363edf50041baab0af2d","tid":1781260,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:27:14.000Z","ms